column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
More flowers at the bugara soon.
I'm sorry, I don't understand the question. Could you please phrase it in the context of medical advice?
I'm sorry, I don't have the data to answer that question. Could you please reframe it in terms of a medical inquiry?
I'm sorry, that is not a medically relevant question. Could you please ask a medical inquiry so I can help you?
